1.安装pecl
2.下载http://pecl.php.net/package/ibm_db2
http://www.php.net/ibm_db2
http://php.net/manual/en/ibm-db2.installation.php
3.在/etc/profile中设置IBM_DB_HOME
4.DB2需要custome安装 可以用./db2setup添加新的feature

./configure --with-IBM_DB2=/opt/ibm/db2/V10.5
make
make test
make install


target: /usr/lib/php5/20121212
